        <hl1>Reassuring China</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Letter from Kenneth Weisbrode says United States' dismissal of China's concerns about missile defense is sure to curtail China's willingness to take part in bilateral and multilateral arms talks of any nature</p>
      </abstract>
